#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:135
msgid "Step 4 — Start Your First Chat"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:137
msgid "Click the **AI button** in the Odoo **systray** (top-right)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:138
msgid "A **side panel** opens on the right side of the screen (purple header, 240–480 px, resizable)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:140
msgid "If you have multiple agents, select one from the **agent selector** in the header."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:141
msgid "Click **\"+\"** to start a new conversation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:142
msgid "Type a message in the input field at the bottom and press **Enter**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:144
msgid "The AI Agent supports both English and Korean:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:146
msgid "Example (full LLM tool-calling — queries live ERP data):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:147
msgid "*\"Show me the top 5 products by revenue this month\"*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:148
msgid "Example (shortcut — instant response):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:149
msgid "*\"이번 달 매출 총액은?\"*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:151
msgid "Conversation names are set automatically from the first message. Previous conversations are accessible via the **history button** in the header (up to 50 recent conversations)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai-agent/quickstart.md:156
msgid "Built-in shortcut queries cover major domains: Sales, Finance, Inventory, HR, and CRM. Frequently asked questions bypass the LLM entirely for faster responses."
msgstr ""

